reviewText: The Wonder Years DVD contains many film clips of well known songs of the 80s and 90s. Disk 2 has the 12" mix of Shiny Shiny by Haysi Fantayzee....they dance and mime to the original 12" mix at a live concert....just wonderful for those who wanted to get a copy of the original 12" mix. Lots of other hidden gems can be found on the DVD and the accompanying CD....CD only has 7" mix of Shiny Shiny.
